Give me the remote.

03:42.755 --> 03:44.856
Here. Let me do this.

03:45.325 --> 03:46.158
What the hell?

03:46.160 --> 03:48.227
It's covered in buttons!
Covered!

03:48.229 --> 03:51.763
Don't bother with the buttons.
Use the voice command.

03:52.532 --> 03:53.966
