04:10.750 --> 04:12.618
Record.

04:12.952 --> 04:13.485
Nothing!

04:13.487 --> 04:15.387
It's not identifying
your voice.

04:15.389 --> 04:16.955
You gotta say your name.

04:16.957 --> 04:19.091
My name is...

04:19.192 --> 04:21.126
Murray...

04:21.194 --> 04:22.527
Goldberg!

04:22.529 --> 04:24.296
(ADAM AND ERICA LAUGHING)

04:24.298 --> 04:26.064
Like it understands him.

04:26.066 --> 04:29.167
All right. Just record
the damn game.

04:30.069 --> 04:30.936
(PANTING) Where is she?

04:30.938 --> 04:33.205
Where's the woman who gave me
life and nothing more, huh?

04:33.207 --> 04:35.841
Whoa, whoa, stop.
I've been waiting for you,

04:35.843 --> 04:37.042
and we need to talk.

04:37.044 --> 04:37.976
Busy. I gotta kill mom.

04:37.978 --> 04:40.112
Um, no. You're coming with me.

04:40.114 --> 04:42.180
Leave me alone,
or so help me God...

04:42.182 --> 04:44.783
Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!

04:44.785 --> 04:47.286
Ow! Ow! Ow!

04:47.654 --> 04:49.254
Why'd you have to
purple my nurple?

