05:13.447 --> 05:14.579
"We're playing
Def Leppard records

05:14.581 --> 05:17.582
and making jiffy pop.
Miss you."

05:17.584 --> 05:18.116
So?

05:18.118 --> 05:22.721
So... I was at a
Def Leppard concert...

05:22.723 --> 05:23.855
In New Jersey.

05:23.857 --> 05:26.491
Jersey?
That's the red zone.

05:26.493 --> 05:27.192
Damn right it is.

05:27.194 --> 05:29.127
Studying with Lainey
was my cover story.

05:29.129 --> 05:32.331
You got a good cover story,
and you can do anything
you want.

05:32.333 --> 05:34.599
I've even been
to Manhattan.

05:34.867 --> 05:35.434
The black zone.

05:35.436 --> 05:38.437
And tomorrow night,
guess where I'm going.

05:38.971 --> 05:39.771
Kegger in the woods.

05:39.773 --> 05:43.408
Whoa! That's supposed to be
the best party of the year.

05:43.410 --> 05:45.377
And my cover story...

05:45.511 --> 05:46.912
(SINGSONGY)
Band practice.

05:46.914 --> 05:49.114
(NORMAL VOICE)
I haven't played violin
since eighth grade,

05:49.116 --> 05:51.183
but she doesn't know that.

05:51.617 --> 05:53.418
No way.
Can I join your band?

05:53.420 --> 05:55.420
I have an electric keyboard
in my closet.

05:55.422 --> 05:56.555
Get your own thing, idiot.

05:56.557 --> 06:00.525
Pfft. Your loss.
It has over
70 rhythm settings.

06:00.527 --> 06:03.662
Has samba,
bossa nova, rap,

06:03.664 --> 06:04.863
has rock 1, has rock 2...

06:04.865 --> 06:09.468
Stop! It's not a real band,
and even if it was,
you suck at keyboard.

06:09.470 --> 06:11.937
