06:37.531 --> 06:38.864
I can only stay
a few minutes.

06:38.866 --> 06:42.534
I got a date
with one of the sisters.

06:42.536 --> 06:44.536
Which one again?
Miriam.

06:44.538 --> 06:45.670
She's the sexy one, right?

06:45.672 --> 06:48.006
