"As seen on TV."

06:56.183 --> 06:59.651
<i>Back in the day,</i>
<i>commercials were simple</i>
<i>and to the point,</i>

06:59.653 --> 07:00.786
<i>especially this classic...</i>

07:00.788 --> 07:04.890
<i>I've fallen,</i>
<i>and I can't get up!</i>

07:04.892 --> 07:07.826
Why is no one helping her?

07:07.828 --> 07:08.326
Help her!

07:08.328 --> 07:10.662
<i>We're sending</i>
<i>help immediately,</i>
<i>Mrs. Fletcher.</i>

07:10.664 --> 07:12.664
Oh, good, they're coming.

07:14.400 --> 07:15.133
Are you kidding me?

07:15.135 --> 07:18.437
Why don't you get me
a sweatshirt
which says "I'm old"

07:18.439 --> 07:20.205
