to the duck pond
to feed the ducks?

07:20.207 --> 07:24.209
Dad, you live alone.
What happens if you fall
and you can't get up?

07:24.211 --> 07:29.815
In my whole life,
I've never once tripped,
slipped, or fallen.

07:29.817 --> 07:32.184
Yeah! This is an insult!

07:32.186 --> 07:34.686
I'm rock solid.
Go ahead.

07:34.688 --> 07:36.588
Sock me in the kidney.
Do it.

07:36.590 --> 07:39.024
Go ahead, mom.
Hit grandpa.

07:39.026 --> 07:39.524
