in the kidney, dad.

07:41.695 --> 07:44.863
You don't want it? Fine.
Be a burden on your family.

07:44.865 --> 07:47.466
I will.
He will.

07:48.034 --> 07:51.536
ADULT ADAM:  <i>While my mom</i>
<i>had her own strategy</i>
<i>to get her way,</i>

07:51.538 --> 07:54.639
<i>Barry was gonna use</i>
<i>Erica's strategy to get his.</i>

07:54.641 --> 07:56.141
ERICA: (LOWERED VOICE)
