enough, but...

08:17.097 --> 08:18.063
I love you, girl.

08:18.065 --> 08:20.131
(MOUTHING WORDS)
(LAUGHS)

08:20.133 --> 08:21.433
I'll tell you what.

08:21.435 --> 08:24.236
You're gonna get some
extra stir-fry tonight.

08:24.238 --> 08:24.970
Oh, I almost forgot.

08:24.972 --> 08:27.706
Can I go to Roger McFadden's
house tomorrow night?

08:27.708 --> 08:28.940
I love Roger McFadden.

08:28.942 --> 08:32.244
