That's why I chose him...

08:32.246 --> 08:33.812
To teach me Spanish.

08:33.814 --> 08:35.680
We have a quiz.

08:35.682 --> 08:37.249
(MOUTHS WORDS)

08:37.251 --> 08:38.717
I'll be home at 10:00,

08:38.719 --> 08:40.752
which is rule four,
if I recall.

08:40.754 --> 08:41.353
And don't worry.

08:41.355 --> 08:44.055
I'll follow all
the other rules, too.

08:44.057 --> 08:47.092
That sounds...  <i>Muy bueno.</i>

08:47.094 --> 08:49.661
Roger will cover
that with you.

08:50.396 --> 08:51.396
(ENGINE STARTS)

08:51.398 --> 08:52.197
