<i>♪ This speech is my recital</i>

08:54.334 --> 08:55.700
<i>♪ I think it's very vital</i>

08:55.702 --> 08:57.802
<i>♪ To rock a rhyme,</i>
<i>that's right on time</i>

08:57.804 --> 08:59.971
<i>♪ "it's tricky" is the...</i>
<i>♪ Here we go</i>

08:59.973 --> 09:02.674
<i>♪ It's tricky to rock a rhyme,</i>
<i>to rock a rhyme</i>

09:02.676 --> 09:05.143
<i>♪ That's right on time,</i>
<i>it's tricky</i>

09:05.145 --> 09:07.812
<i>♪ It's tricky,</i>
<i>tricky, tricky, oh</i>

