<i>♪ It's tricky to rock a rhyme,</i>
<i>to rock a rhyme</i>

09:10.217 --> 09:13.018
<i>♪ That's right on time,</i>
<i>it's tricky</i>

09:13.020 --> 09:14.553
<i>♪ Tricky, tricky,</i>
<i>tricky, tricky</i>

09:14.555 --> 09:17.722
<i>♪ In New York, the people talk</i>
<i>and try to make us rhyme</i>

09:17.724 --> 09:19.891
<i>♪ They really hawk</i>
