09:19.893 --> 09:22.327
<i>♪ Because we have no time</i>
<i>(LAUGHS)</i>

09:22.329 --> 09:24.829
<i>♪ And in the city...</i>
<i>Wow.</i>

09:24.831 --> 09:28.600
My God. Look who made it
out of the green zone.

09:28.602 --> 09:30.635
All thanks to you.
Oh.

09:30.637 --> 09:33.204
Now point me to the phone
and we're good to go.

09:33.206 --> 09:34.773
What are you talking about?

09:34.775 --> 09:35.307
Gotta call mom,

09:35.309 --> 09:39.444
tell her I arrived safely
at "Roger McFadden's house."

09:39.446 --> 09:41.046
There's no phone here.

09:41.048 --> 09:44.049
It's the kegger in the woods.
The woods?

09:44.051 --> 09:44.449
Well...

09:44.451 --> 09:46.184
There's gotta be a house
here somewhere.

09:46.186 --> 09:50.622
I mean, a lumberjack's camp.
A Ranger's station.

09:50.624 --> 09:51.489
A secret army base.

09:51.491 --> 09:53.191
How deep in the woods
do you think we are?

09:53.193 --> 09:55.560
I don't know.
This is the orange zone.

09:55.562 --> 09:57.929
I've never gone this far.
Calm down.

09:57.931 --> 10:00.131
You told Roger McFadden
all about this, right?

10:00.133 --> 10:02.834
No. Roger went down
the shore with his family.

10:02.836 --> 10:06.571
You need him to cover for you
in case mom calls his house.

10:06.573 --> 10:08.206
What do you think
"Cover story" means?

10:08.208 --> 10:10.675
It means someone
to cover for you!

10:10.677 --> 10:12.577
You wanted other people
involved?

10:12.579 --> 10:14.946
This is too
complicated for me!

10:14.948 --> 10:16.481
You should have just
let me join your band!

10:16.483 --> 10:19.017
Dumbass, you're gonna
ruin this for the both of us!

10:19.019 --> 10:22.621
Get in your car
and drive to a phone now.

10:24.290 --> 10:26.057
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

10:26.059 --> 10:28.660
Gotta call my mom,
gotta call mom.

10:28.662 --> 10:30.762
Oh, no, no, no!

10:33.699 --> 10:35.367
Damn it!
(STARTS ENGINE)

10:35.369 --> 10:37.402
I gotta call my mom!

10:41.741 --> 10:44.142
Erica! Help me!

10:44.144 --> 10:46.378
Let's go over there.

10:47.179 --> 10:48.780
Damn it.

10:50.383 --> 10:51.549
Why?

10:51.551 --> 10:55.086
I gotta call my mom!
I gotta call my mom!

10:55.088 --> 10:56.988
I gotta call my mom!

10:59.091 --> 10:59.724
