10:59.726 --> 11:01.493
ADULT ADAM:
<i>Back before e-mails,</i>
<i>texts, and tweets,</i>

11:01.495 --> 11:03.061
<i>you could go a whole day</i>
<i>without spoilers</i>

11:03.063 --> 11:04.229
<i>or knowing the score</i>
<i>of a game,</i>

11:04.231 --> 11:06.364
<i>and now my dad was finally</i>
<i>gonna get to watch</i>

11:06.366 --> 11:09.834
<i>the most important</i>
<i>Phillies game of his lifetime.</i>

11:09.836 --> 11:10.735
